{"tid":1645220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇FC- 司機傳聞：冒警捉少女上車，射完即棄","createTime":"2019-10-10T21:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:23:53.000Z","uid":294333,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"40779d3f0f258a3d36cef7b4d1d3c16a6a155d23","tid":1645220,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:04:22.000Z","msg":"半個月前諗住出post，不過P牌限每日一post，又費事心涉嫌P牌狗帶風向，而且道聽途說，冇Fact check<br />\n<br />\n不過今日爆15歲女浮屍，或者有啲關聯.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大排檔式茶餐廳，午飯時間，啲司機大佬食飯吹水時，笑鳩警察嘅說話<br />\n大概內容：<br />\n<br />\n1. 警察可以冒充示威者，又唔使表明警員身份出示委任證，香港治安已經無法無天，隻手遮天<br />\n<br />\n2. 無雞叫：10.1 大陸國慶前，大陸嚴打雞竇，香港晚晚搞事堵路，散水都搞到凌晨2，3點，香港啲雞都瞓晒落晒妝，<br />\n<br />\n3. 半夜兜下車，用毛巾蓋口，拉貼牆紙單仃女仔上車，<br />\n<br />\n4. 完事後班傻仔實認為黑警做，唔敢報警，<br />\n<br />\n5. 就算<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">掟咗落海都無警察受理，</span></span></strong>警察依家咁敵視班學生，玩玩玩，實扮無事結案算"},{"pid":"64d411f02acb0a1de116fea73f6e301262f23726","tid":1645220,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:05:01.000Z","msg":"尋晚嘅新聞，根本瞓唔到覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e892c6bd70861f6c0389b13b98281fa43da66fea","tid":1645220,"uid":163959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:06:02.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦p牌警犬<br />\n自己鳩up扮茶餐廳收風"},{"pid":"df663b7eb10cdcbf6ccb166c417b052ca43808b9","tid":1645220,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e892c6bd70861f6c0389b13b98281fa43da66fea","tid":1645220,"uid":163959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:06:02.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦p牌警犬<br />\n自己鳩up扮茶餐廳收風"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T21:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" clas